 Name:            PGA Tour Golf III

 Genre:           Golf-Sport

 Hardware needed: 8MB RAM (+5MB of VM), 256color-screenmode

 Software needed: System 7.1

 Description:     "Very good graphics..."

 Tested on:       A4000, Cyberstorm040/40MHz, Kick/WB3.0, Cybervision64,
